both cases show an improved heat transfer compared to the\nbaseline designs. For the shell-and-tube case, the full freedom topology\noptimization approach is shown to yield performance improvements of up to 113%\nunder the same pressure drop.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2020 15:28:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 07:43:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-07"}
